snippet.title: Margot Robbie Pirates of the Caribbean Spin-Off! Redd? Depp?!
snippet.description:
Margot Robbie Pirates of the Caribbean today! Beyond The Trailer's reaction & breakdown of news Margot Robbie & Birds of Prey screenwriter Christina Hodson! Redd? Depp's Jack Sparrow for Pirates of the Caribbean 6?
http://bit.ly/subscribeBTT

Margot Robbie Pirates of the Caribbean today! Beyond The Trailer host Grace Randolph's reaction and breakdown of news that Margot Robbie will star in a Pirates of the Caribbean spin-off for Disney, with Birds of Prey screenwriter Christina Hodson! Is Robbie playing Redd? Will Johnny Depp be in the other Pirates of the Caribbean 6? Share your own reaction to a Margot Robbie Pirates of the Caribbean spin-off before you see the full movie!  And be sure to make Beyond The Trailer your first stop for movie and entertainment news here on YouTube today!

Interact with host & creator Grace Randolph!
